tiers.ability_description: Whenever Dark Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
The first time each Hutt Cartel ally falls below 50% Health, all Hutt Cartel allies reduce their cooldowns by 1 and gain 10% Turn Meter.

The max cooldown of Muscle In is reduced by 2. If the ally in the Leader slot is Hutt Cartel and not Gamorrean Guard, whenever they use an ability, Gamorrean Guard assists. Whenever Gamorrean Guard inflicts Damage Over Time on an enemy, there is a 50% chance to inflict an additional Damage Over Time for 3 turns and Hutt Cartel allies gain 10% Max Health (max 50%) and Max Protection (max 50%) (once per turn).
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn, for each enemy with fewer than 4 debuffs, that ally gains 30% Potency until the end of the turn.
Whenever a Scoundrel ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Blinded, inflict Blind for 2 turns on the enemy, which can't be resisted.
Whenever Veteran Smuggler Han Solo critically hits an enemy, Veteran Smuggler Han Solo gains 10% Critical Damage, Defense Penetration, and Offense (stacking, max 200%) until the end of battle.

Whenever IG-11 uses an ability, they deal more damage (max 100%) equal to half their Potency percentage. This effect will only trigger if IG-11 has more than 0% Potency.

At the start of their first turn, Empire allies gain Offense equal to 400% of their current Defense. Then they lose 50% Defense.

At the start of battle, Imperial Probe Droid loses all Protection and gains that much Max Health. Imperial Probe Droid can be revived after using Self-Destruct and ignores Taunt.  Whenever Imperial Probe Droid uses Self-Destruct, the target enemy takes additional True damage equal to 50% of Imperial Probe Droid's Max Health, which can't be evaded.

Whenever Rebel Fighter allies lose a stack of Heal Over Time, they gain a stack of Heal Over Time (10%) for 2 turns.

Whenever Rebel Fighter allies grant a buff to another ally, that ally gains 10% Turn Meter (limit once per turn per ally).
